<h3>M17N (Multilingualization)</h3>
<p>
Starting with the 0.5-Release the Koch-Suite uses an easy and extensible
M17N-framework. A German, English and a preliminary Spanish language module 
is included. Modules for other languages may be easily created. 
</p>

